&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;London salary - £45,753 - £51,668 plus HCAS £6,890.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Leeds salary- £45,753 - £51,668.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We have an exciting opportunity for two Finance Business Partners to join within NHS Resolution. Both are permanent posts.The post holders will be accountable to Head of Management Accounting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The post holders will be responsible for:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;• Providing comprehensive management accounting and business partnering service to individual operational directorates. Providing robust financial support, advice and challenge for specific business areas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;• Undertaking a lead role on providing financial data for the management and development of information reporting and analysis, in line with regulatory requirements. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;• Providing expert financial leadership, advice and support to budget holders with regards to service development proposals.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;• Working as a member of the finance team ensuring high standards of financial control.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;For an informal discussion about the post please contact Sarah Reed via sarah.reed@resolution.nhs.uk &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The closing date is 12 November 2020&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Interview date is between 17 November and 4 December&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;In response to the Government advice relating to the Covid-19 pandemic our staff and teams in all business areas are fully supported in working remotely. All new employees will also be provided with the necessary training and equipment to work from home and we have put in place additional measures to support new employees during this period.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note that the closing and interview dates for roles may be subject to change to take into account any Government advice relating to Covid-19.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
